This Connect 4 project was made by Kuir Aguer, Brendan Duke, Jean Ferreira, 
Zachariah Levine and Pranesh Satish.

SDL2 is required to compile and run this program, and can be installed with
your package manager or compiled from source from https://www.libsdl.org/.

To compile: cd to the Connect_4/code/ directory and type "make all".
The ../build/ directory will be created automatically.

To run: cd to the Connect_4/build/ directory and type "./sdl2_connect4".
